OL,3,CSiblings separated during the war have
OL,4,Cbeen reunited after 80 years
OL,6,FJennifer Buck went along to the family
OL,7,Freunion with Ronnie, June and May
OL,9,FIt is more than 80 years since May has
OL,10,Fsat and chatted with her brother and
OL,11,Fsister.
OL,13,FAt the age of just 16 months she was
OL,14,Fevacuated from Manchester and put on a
OL,15,Ftrain to Brighouse in Yorkshire.
OL,17,FDuring the second world war she
OL,18,Fremembers coming back to Manchester to
OL,19,Fsee her family, but at the age of six,
OL,20,Fthe couple she was living with wanted
OL,21,Fto adopt her.
