OL,4,Cbeen reunited after 80 years
OL,6,FHer sister June said it was a
OL,7,Fdifficult decision for their Mum.
OL,9,F"It was awful, we always wanted to get
OL,10,Fher back and I've just been told that
OL,11,Fmy Mum said it was the worst mistake
OL,12,Fshe had ever made"
OL,14,FOver the years, they have all spent
OL,15,Ftime looking for each other and have
OL,16,Fnever forgotten their close ties.
