OL,3,CSiblings separated during the war have
OL,4,Cbeen reunited after 80 years
OL,6,FIt wasn't until 2024 when June's
OL,7,Fdaughter Gaynor started looking into
OL,8,Fthe family tree and was linked up to
OL,9,FMay through a family member.
OL,11,FWhen they met up Ronnie said it was
OL,12,Fvery emotional
OL,14,F"I sat by her all the time, hugged her
OL,15,Fand kissed her and was introduced to
OL,16,Fher children"
OL,18,FJune, who was just a baby when May was
OL,19,Fevacuated said the family connection
OL,20,Fwas obvious straight away.
